These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, indian, canadian, german, spanish, indonesian, brazilian
1. the indian is in the middle##1
2. the indian is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the german##1
4. the polish is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the brazilian is on the far left##1
6. the indonesian is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | german | spanish | indian | canadian | polish | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  security-guard, writer, project-manager, architect, software-developer, fisherman, social-worker
1. the social-worker is on the far right##1
2. the security-guard is on the far left##1
3. the security-guard is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the project-manager##1
5. the architect is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the social-worker is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | security-guard | software-developer | project-manager | fisherman | architect | writer | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, puzzles, dancing, camping, baking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | camping | hiking | baking | puzzles | collecting | traveling | dancing |

 #################################

 
