1. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | cat | fish | rabbit | horse | ferret | rat |

