.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, family, fantasy, epic, romance, mystery, adventure
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | family | documentary | mystery | epic | adventure | fantasy |

